  "text": "A previous protocol was followed with modifications [CITATION_1] . HeLa cells were transfected with pcDNA3/Flag-mTOR. Immunoprecipitated (IPed) Flag-mTOR by Flag antibodyconjugated agarose (Sigma) was incubated with recombinant GST-AKT and purified recombinant His-YY1 wt or DOPB mutant in a kinase buffer (25 mM HEPES, pH 7.5, 100 mM KAc, 1 mM MgCl 2 ) at 378C for 20 min. The samples were then analyzed by western blots for pAKT(S473) levels.",
